cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method to improve the performance of classification algorithms by selecting relevant features. This falls under the category of machine learning and data mining (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method involves filtering and resampling the sample domain, which is a common technique in data mining (cs.DM). The experiments carried out on different types of datasets also involve image classification (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
